### Read: すべての投稿を取得
GET http://localhost:8080/posts HTTP/1.1

### Read: 特定の投稿を取得
GET http://localhost:8080/posts/1 HTTP/1.1

### Create: 新しい投稿を作成
POST http://localhost:8080/posts HTTP/1.1 content-type: application/json
{
"title": "新しい投稿",
"content": "投稿の内容です",
"likes": 10 }

### Update: 特定の投稿を更新
PUT http://localhost:8080/posts/1 HTTP/1.1 content-type: application/json
{
"title": "新しい投稿 update", "content": "投稿の内容です update", "likes": 11
}

### Delete: 特定の投稿を削除
DELETE http://localhost:8080/posts/1 HTTP/1.1